section "mod-tome/data/zones/tannen-tower/zone.lua"

t("Tannen's Tower", "Tour de Tannen", "_t")
t("The portal brought you to what seems to be a cell in the basement of the tower. You must escape!", "Le portail vous a mené dans une cellule au sous-sol. Il faut s'échapper, quelle corvée.", "_t")
t("As you climb up the steps, you see Tannen standing with his drolem, reading a scrap of parchment. As he reads, his eyes grow wider, and he starts sweating and pacing back and forth. When he reaches to stuff it in his pocket, he sees you and jumps back like a startled cat. \"No! Not now! You have no idea what's at stake!\" He retrieves a fistful of brightly-colored flasks from his robes, and his drolem's eyes glow as it springs to life, metal screeching in an impressive imitation of a roar.", "En montant les marches, vous voyez Tannen avec son drolem, lisant un parchemin. Il sue, il panique, il s'agite. Il vous voit et saute comme un chat effrayé. \"Non ! Pas maintenant ! Vous ne comprenez rien !\" Il sort des fioles colorées, son drolem s'anime avec un cri métallique. Bref, une scène de théâtre de bas étage.", "_t")

