t("This helmet radiates a dark power. Its visor seems to twist and corrupt the vision of its wearer. You feel worried that if you were to lower it for long, the visions may affect your mind.", "Ce heaume irradie un pouvoir sombre. Sa visière semble déformer et corrompre la vision de celui qui le porte. Vous craignez qu'en l'abaissant trop longtemps, les visions ne finissent par affecter votre esprit.", "_t")
t("Umbral Razor", "Rasoir Ombral", "entity name")
